   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "404.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "407.520", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich der Generationengerechtigkeit verpflichtet wei\u00df."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "407.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "411.560", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen erg\u00e4nzen wir die rentenpolitischen Ma\u00dfnahmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "411.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "415.080", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir kurzfristig im Hinblick auf die M\u00fctterrente, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "415.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "422.280", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Erwerbsminderungsrente und eine Grundrente oberhalb des Grundsicherungsniveaus ergreifen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "422.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "424.880", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch die Arbeit einer Rentenkommission, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "424.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "427.200", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Frage in den Blick nehmen soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "427.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "435.000", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
