   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "491.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "496.800", 
   "id": "s000151", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein gro\u00dfes Interesse an einer langfristigen Planbarkeit durch einen nachhaltigen Rentenkonsens\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "496.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "502.720", 
   "id": "s000152", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so wird dieses Thema n\u00e4mlich dem wahlterminbezogenen Streit zwischen den Parteien entzogen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "502.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "503.920", 
   "id": "s000153", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "503.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "505.840", 
   "id": "s000154", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir jedenfalls sind bereit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "505.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "508.120", 
   "id": "s000155", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau daran zu arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "508.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "509.320", 
   "id": "s000156", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
